      • findFirstAvailability

        public Availability findFirstAvailability(ActivityType activityType,
                                          int duration,
                                          java.util.ArrayList<BlockType> blockTypes,
                                          java.util.ArrayList<java.lang.Integer> daysForbidden,
                                          java.util.ArrayList<Activity> activitiesToAvoid,
                                          Date dateLowerBound,
                                          Date dateUpperBound)
        Parameters:
        activityType - for which you wish to find an availability
        duration - of the availability at minimal
        blockTypes - the availability must be in a block of one of those types
        daysForbidden - list of integer between 0 and 6, of forbidden days for the availability
        activitiesToAvoid - list of activities to avoid, the availability returned should not overlap any of those activities
        dateLowerBound - date at which we start to find the availability, included
        dateUpperBound - last possible date of the availability, included
        Returns:
        the first availability in this schedule, respecting the constraints linked to the inputs
